reviewText: Perfect and very good quality, I loved it, thanks

The Julio Iglesias "En Espana" DVD was a gift for my Uncle- he had indicated that he was having problems obtaining a DVD and I was able to obtain it for him via amazon.com; he is enjoying this DVD immensely.  Thanks for having it available.
Had to buy a region-free DVD player to play it. Not the best quality, but still provides a good glimpse of Julio performing in his prime.

I bought this product but I had to return it because of its specification.  It seems this DVD is for Zone 2 (Europe) because I could not use it in my DVD Player which was bought here in the US.  The seller should specify this condition in the description of the product to avoid the problems associated with returning a product.  I had not returned a product before this DVD and sometimes you do not have time to do this so I prefer to avoid this as much as possible.  If I see this DVD available for my region (USA), I would buy it.
Live in Jerusalem The scenery of Spain is beautiful but the concert is average.
